# Documentation Standards

## üìö DOCUMENTATION STANDARDS

This project maintains comprehensive documentation with strict standards for consistency and usability.

### **Required Document Sections**

**Core Document Structure:**
```markdown
# Document Title

## TL;DR
Brief summary of the document's purpose and key points.

## Purpose
Clear explanation of what this document covers and why it exists.

## Usage
How to use the information or tools described in this document.

## Owner
AI Development Team - [Specific Role/Component]

## Last Reviewed
YYYY-MM-DD

## Governance Status
| Category | Violations | Status |
|----------|------------|--------|
| archive | 0 | ‚úÖ Clean |
| shadow_fork | 0 | ‚úÖ Clean |
| readme | 0 | ‚úÖ Clean |
| multirep | 0 | ‚úÖ Clean |

*Last updated: YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM UTC*
```

